04:44.267 --> 04:47.187
A man standing in the park
across the street.

04:47.478 --> 04:49.678
- Seen him before.
- How can you tell?

04:49.939 --> 04:52.779
You're blind without your glasses.
Where are your glasses?

04:53.067 --> 04:55.787
- In the bedroom.
- You're running out of time.

04:56.154 --> 04:57.954
- You know how blind I am...

