4421 Gainsborough.

06:08.729 --> 06:11.809
Send DCPD. Set up a perimeter.
Tell them we're en route.

06:12.108 --> 06:15.828
I was thinking maybe I'd play hooky,
stay home today.

06:16.488 --> 06:20.128
- "We've come to dedicate a portion..."
- What do you think?

06:20.451 --> 06:23.491
