06:48.312 --> 06:52.352
Chief! We got a problem
with our location.

06:56.738 --> 06:58.618
- It's no longer there.
- Shit!

06:58.865 --> 07:00.785
- Time frame?
- Thirteen minutes.

07:01.035 --> 07:02.955
Investigator from the fed's here.

07:03.203 --> 07:05.563
I don't need some twink
from the fed poking around.

07:05.831 --> 07:07.311
I wrote it on your calendar.

07:07.541 --> 07:09.861
See if the neighbors knew
where they went.

07:10.128 --> 07:11.968
- Check all relations.
- Checking.

07:12.212 --> 07:16.372
Just get him some coffee,
tell him how I save your ass every day.

07:16.801 --> 07:18.161
I got coffee, thanks.

07:18.386 --> 07:20.946
Danny Witwer,
the twink from the fed.

07:21.222 --> 07:22.982
Oops. Gum?

07:23.224 --> 07:25.624
I'll give you the full tour
some other time.

07:25.894 --> 07:29.694
They moved two weeks ago. Nobody
knows where. Still searching for family.

07:30.023 --> 07:31.663
Time horizon, 12 minutes.

07:31.984 --> 07:33.984
He's scrubbing the image, looking for...

07:34.153 --> 07:36.433
...clues as to where
the murder will happen.

07:36.696 --> 07:41.656
Original running bond brick pattern,
Georgian details. Brick was repointed.

07:42.912 --> 07:47.632
And that this nation, under God,
shall not perish from the earth.

07:48.084 --> 07:50.604
Victims are pronounced here,
killers here.

07:50.879 --> 07:55.159
