09:08.418 --> 09:10.258
Merry-go-round.

09:10.879 --> 09:12.199
It's a park.

09:15.884 --> 09:19.164
There's only 16 of these old
merry-go-rounds left in the city.

09:19.471 --> 09:22.071
Two in Georgetown, one in
Barnaby Woods, the others in Woodley.

09:22.349 --> 09:24.869
