Time horizon, six minutes.

10:41.599 --> 10:43.599
Let's go to bed.

10:43.976 --> 10:45.856
Let's do it in here.

10:47.230 --> 10:50.430
- But the bed is soft.
- I'm soft.

11:36.573 --> 11:37.933
Shit.

11:39.617 --> 11:40.977
Which one is it?

11:47.667 --> 11:50.307
- Not the bed.
- Come on.

11:50.587 --> 11:52.787
I don't want to be on the bed.

11:56.301 --> 12:00.381
- We're catching up to the future.
- Shut up, Evanna. Jad?

12:01.057 --> 12:03.217
