12:40.890 --> 12:43.330
I forgot my glasses.

12:43.602 --> 12:44.682
Howard.

12:56.573 --> 12:58.693
You know how blind I am without them.

13:00.244 --> 13:02.004
Howard, don't cry.

13:02.454 --> 13:03.494
Marks!

13:22.642 --> 13:24.402
Look at me. Look at me.

13:29.399 --> 13:31.479
Positive for Howard Marks.

13:31.735 --> 13:34.855
By mandate of the District of Columbia
Precrime Division...

13:35.155 --> 13:39.195
...you're under arrest for the future
murder of Mrs. Marks and Mr. Dubin...

13:39.535 --> 13:42.895
...that was to take place today
at 0800 hours and four minutes.

13:43.205 --> 13:46.965
- I didn't do anything. Sarah?
- Give the man his hat.

13:47.293 --> 13:51.453
Oh, God.
Don't put that halo on me. Sarah!

13:51.797 --> 13:56.197
- Put your hand on your head.
- Help me! I wasn't gonna do anything!

13:56.553 --> 13:59.193
I'm Officer Scott with the
Precrime Trauma Response Unit.

13:59.472 --> 14:01.712
Sit here a minute and listen to me.

14:01.975 --> 14:04.735
Your husband is being arrested
by Precrime.

14:05.020 --> 14:07.740
Oh, God, Howard, no.

14:08.190 --> 14:12.350
Howard, don't cry.
Howard, don't cry.

14:15.280 --> 14:20.080
Please, don't cry.
Oh, God. Oh, God.

14:22.454 --> 14:24.854
I thought they stopped the murder.

14:25.416 --> 14:29.376
That's just an echo.
Pre-Cog deja vu, if you will.

14:29.713 --> 14:32.873
The really bad ones
the Pre-Cogs see over and over again.

14:33.174 --> 14:35.334
Wally, erase the incoming.

14:50.317 --> 14:53.117
Imagine a world without murder.

14:54.155 --> 14:56.115
- I lost my best friend.
- I lost my aunt.

14:56.407 --> 14:58.407
- I lost my dad.
- I lost my wife.

14:58.743 --> 15:03.183
Just six years ago, the homicide rate
had reached epidemic proportions.

15:03.706 --> 15:06.546
It seemed that only a miracle
could stop the bloodshed.

15:06.876 --> 15:10.916
But instead of one miracle, we
were given three: The Pre-Cognitives.

15:11.297 --> 15:13.977
Within just one month
under the Precrime program...

15:14.301 --> 15:17.741
...the murder rate in the District
of Columbia was reduced 90%% .

15:18.097 --> 15:20.137
- They were waiting for me.
- He was gonna rape me.

15:20.432 --> 15:22.192
- I was going to be stabbed.
- Right here.

15:22.434 --> 15:26.794
Within a year, Precrime effectively
stopped murder in our nation 's capital.

15:27.230 --> 15:29.270
In the six years of our experiment...

15:30.735 --> 15:32.975
...there hasn't been a single murder.

15:33.237 --> 15:35.357
And now Precrime can work for you.

15:35.698 --> 15:38.458
We want to make certain
that every American...

15:38.785 --> 15:41.745
...can bank on the infallibility
of the system.

15:42.205 --> 15:47.365
And to ensure that what keeps us safe
will also keep us free.

15:48.921 --> 15:50.881
- Precrime. It works.
- It works.

15:51.172 --> 15:52.492
- It works.
- It works.

15:52.716 --> 15:54.316
- It works.
- It works.

15:54.968 --> 15:57.248
Precrime. It works.

15:57.596 --> 16:02.356
